data.description: Step into this exquisite 2,306 sq ft Spanish Villa-style home where Elegance and comfort seamlessly emerge. The open concept living area boasts high, wood beamed ceilings, allowing natural light to flood the space. A cozy fireplace with Cantera stone with handcrafted mantel creates a focal point for gatherings. The Master suite is a sanctuary of tranquility, boasting a private en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub, separate shower, and dual vanities. Entertainment is at the forefront of this homes design, with a dedicated theater room. This Villa style residence is more than just a house, its a place of comfort, luxury and entertainment coverage to create the perfect retreat for those who appreciate the finer things in life. Make this Home your own today
